crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: ET INFO Executable Download from dotted-quad Host

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: ET INFO Dotted Quad Host DLL Request
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert http $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET any (msg:"ET INFO Dotted Quad Host DLL Request"; flow:established,from_client; flowbits:isset,http.dottedquadhost; flowbits:set,http.dottedquadhost.dll; flowbits:unset,http.dottedquadhost; http.request_line; content:".dll HTTP/1."; nocase; fast_pattern; classtype:bad-unknown; sid:2027250; rev:4; metadata:attack_target Client_Endpoint, created_at 2019_04_23, deployment Perimeter, former_category INFO, performance_impact Moderate, signature_severity Minor, updated_at 2020_04_08;)

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: ET INFO Dotted Quad Host PDF Request

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: FILE pdf claimed, but not pdf
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert http any any -> any any (msg:"FILE pdf claimed, but not pdf"; flow:established,to_client; fileext:"pdf"; filemagic:!"PDF document"; filestore; sid:22; rev:1;)
alert icmp $EXTERNAL_NET any -> $HOME_NET any ( msg:"PROTOCOL-ICMP Echo Reply"; icode:0; itype:0; metadata:ruleset community; classtype:misc-activity; sid:408; rev:8; )

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: POLICY-OTHER HTTP request by IPv4 address attempt
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert tcp any any -> any $HTTP_PORTS ( msg:"POLICY-OTHER HTTP request by IPv4 address attempt"; flow:to_server,established; http_header; content:"Host:",fast_pattern,nocase; pcre:"/^Host\x3a\s*(?:(?:25[0-5]|2[0-4][0-9]|[01]?[0-9]?[0-9])\.){3}(?:25[0-5]|2[0-4][0-9]|[01]?[0-9]?[0-9])\s*:?\s*\d*\s*$/smi"; service:http; reference:url,www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec15.html; classtype:policy-violation; sid:50447; rev:1; )
